# i18n directory boundary (`i18n/`, `lib/i18n/`, `messages/`)

## Stack

- **`next-intl`** with **`localePrefix: "always"`** — public URLs are `/{locale}/…` (e.g. `/en/o/acme/apps/contacts`; bare `/en/o` resolves the active org slug via `app/[locale]/o/page.tsx`).
- **Next.js 16** edge entry: [`proxy.ts`](../../proxy.ts) (not `middleware.ts`). Compose **`createIntlMiddleware(routing)`** with narrow product logic only.
- Narrative (proxy + auth cookie gate + resilience): **`AGENTS.md` §5** — *Locale-first application surface*.

## Path builders (locale-aware by construction)

- **`toLocalePath(locale, "/segment")`** in [`lib/i18n/locales.shared.ts`](../../lib/i18n/locales.shared.ts) — first argument is always **`AppLocale`**; never emit bare `/o` or `/sign-in` from server redirects or emails.
- **Root recovery (outside `[locale]`):** [`DEFAULT_LOCALE_HOME_PATH`](../../lib/i18n/root-default-locale-href.shared.ts) for `app/not-found`, `app/error`, and `app/global-error` — same default-locale home as [`app/page.tsx`](../../app/page.tsx) redirect; use `next/link` with `prefetch={false}` there (not `#i18n/navigation`).
- **`toLocaleRoutePattern("/segment")`** → `"/[locale]/segment"` for **`revalidatePath(..., "page")`** so all locales invalidate (Next.js dynamic segment pattern).
- **`toLocaleOrgAppsRevalidatePattern("/contacts")`** → `"/[locale]/o/[orgSlug]/apps/contacts"` for ERP **`revalidatePath`** (all locales + org slugs).
- **`ensureAppLocale(params.locale)`** for `app/[locale]/…` **RSC** `params`.
- **`getRequestAppLocale()`** in [`lib/i18n/request-locale.server.ts`](../../lib/i18n/request-locale.server.ts) for **Server Actions** / guards without route `params` (wraps `getLocale()`).
- **`sanitizePathAfterOrgSlug`** in [`lib/i18n/dashboard-org-path.shared.ts`](../../lib/i18n/dashboard-org-path.shared.ts) — forwarded-path tail sanitizer for `/o/{slug}/…` redirects.
- **`localePrefixedOrgAppsRedirect`** in [`lib/i18n/dashboard-org-redirect.server.ts`](../../lib/i18n/dashboard-org-redirect.server.ts) — canonical org slug redirect preserving sanitized tail.
- **`searchParamFirst` / `searchParamPositiveInt`** in [`lib/i18n/app-search-params.shared.ts`](../../lib/i18n/app-search-params.shared.ts) — awaited `searchParams` parsing for RSC pages.
- **`PRIVATE_SURFACE_ROBOTS`** in [`lib/i18n/private-surface-robots.shared.ts`](../../lib/i18n/private-surface-robots.shared.ts) — `metadata.robots` for auth/IAM/private shells.

Forbidden:

```txt
redirect("/o")
redirect("/sign-in")
revalidatePath("/en/o/acme/apps/contacts")  // only one locale — use pattern + "page"
```

## Navigation

- Client: **`Link`**, **`useRouter`**, **`usePathname`** from [`#i18n/navigation`](../../i18n/navigation.tsx) (locale-internal `href` like `/o/acme/apps/contacts`). `Link` defaults **`prefetch={false}`**; pass **`prefetch={true}`** to opt in.
- Server RSC redirects: **`redirect` from `next/navigation`** + **`toLocalePath(locale, …)`** (or `ensureAppLocale` + `params`).

## Callbacks and auth

- **`callbackUrl`** query values must be **locale-prefixed** same-origin paths (`/en/...`). Validation: [`resolvePostAuthCallbackUrl`](../../lib/auth/callback-path.ts) + [`stripLeadingLocalePrefix`](../../lib/i18n/locales.shared.ts).
- Interruption URLs: [`authInterruptionHref`](../../lib/auth/auth-interruption-url.shared.ts) requires **`locale: AppLocale`** (no module-level locale capture).

## Config

- Plugin: [`next.config.ts`](../../next.config.ts) → **`createNextIntlPlugin("./i18n/request.ts")`**.
- Routing: [`i18n/routing.ts`](../../i18n/routing.ts) — **`defineRouting`**, single source of locales from [`APP_LOCALES`](../../lib/i18n/locales.shared.ts).
- Request: [`i18n/request.ts`](../../i18n/request.ts) — **`server-only`**, `messages`, optional **`formats`**, **`timeZone`**, **`onError`**, **`getMessageFallback`**.
- Types: [`i18n/global.d.ts`](../../i18n/global.d.ts) augments **`next-intl`** `AppConfig` (`Locale`, `Messages`, `Formats`).

## Proxy

- [`proxy.ts`](../../proxy.ts): forwards **`x-afenda-locale`** ([`AFENDA_LOCALE_HEADER`](../../lib/i18n/locale-header.shared.ts)) for root [`app/layout.tsx`](../../app/layout.tsx) `<html lang>`. Keep matcher excluding **`api`**, **`_next`**, **`_vercel`**, static files.

## Messages

- Catalogs: **`messages/<locale>.json`**. Add namespaces incrementally; auth shell uses **`Auth`**, **`AuthStatus`**, **`CheckEmail`**, **`VerifyEmail`** where wired.

## Refactor gate (temporary)

English-only **active** locales during large refactors — **not** a routing disable. Canonical: **`docs/decisions/0028-single-locale-refactor-gate.md`**.

```env
# .env.config → pnpm env:sync — local dev only; never CI/Vercel production
AFENDA_I18N_SINGLE_LOCALE=1
NEXT_PUBLIC_AFENDA_I18N_SINGLE_LOCALE=1
```

- Shrinks **`APP_LOCALES`** to `["en"]`; **`FULL_APP_LOCALES`** stays four for types/Orama.
- Before deploy: turn off both vars, sync env, backfill `messages/zh-CN.json` / `vi` / `ms`, run **`pnpm lint:fixtures-parity`** and **`pnpm verify:parallel`**.

When unsure, follow **Context7** `/amannn/next-intl` and **Next.js** `revalidatePath` docs for dynamic `[locale]` segments.
